Package com.jesusnut.annotations

Annotation Type FrameworkAnnotation

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(METHOD)
@Documented
public @interface FrameworkAnnotation
    Framework Annotation is user built annotation which is annotated on top of test methods to log the author details and category details to the extent report. 
     
 It is mandatory to annotate every test method with
 "@FrameworkAnnotation{}" or we will get NPE.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Abhishek Bhardwaj-JesusNut
    See Also:
    Author, Category

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      Author author
      Strores ONLY a single author who created the test; from a specified set of Authors in Author; .
      Category[] category
      Strores an array of category to which a test case belongs to; from a specified set of Category in Category; .
      Default value is set, for the scenario if no category is provided for a test method while annotating it with FrameworkAnnotation.
      Include new test categories in Category.

    • Element Detail

      • author

        Author author
        Strores ONLY a single author who created the test; from a specified set of Authors in Author; .
         NOTE : Only a single author can be assigned to a test case/test method in JesusNut Framework.
        Default value is set, for the scenario if no author is provided for a test method while annotating it with FrameworkAnnotation.
        Include new authors/team memebrs in Author.
        Returns:
        Author
        Default:
        com.jesusnut.enums.Author.ABHISHEK

      • category

        Category[] category
        Strores an array of category to which a test case belongs to; from a specified set of Category in Category; .
        Default value is set, for the scenario if no category is provided for a test method while annotating it with FrameworkAnnotation.
        Include new test categories in Category.
        Returns:
        array of Category
        Default:
        {com.jesusnut.enums.Category.REGRESSION}
